You can include snippets without wiki interpretation:

::

  class Module(Folder):

    def view(self):
      print u"Hello, world!"

    `This will not be interpreted`_

For a list of all possibilities like footnotes, tables, etc. `see the
documentation`_. You can also use the toolbar.

